ft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=South+China+Morning+Post&amp;rft.atitle=Karl+May+Museum+under+fire+over+display+of+Native+American+scalps&amp;rft.date=2014-03-11&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.scmp.com%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Farticle%2F1446600%2Fkarl-may-museum-under-fire-over-display-native-american-scalps&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AKarl+May+Museum\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-WildWest-8\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-WildWest_8-0\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation news\">Knight, Ben (10 March 2014). <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.dw.de/wild-west-museum-in-row-over-native-american-scalps/a-17498259\">\"Wild West museum in row over Native American scalps\"</a>. <i>Deutsche Welle</i><span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">3 May</span> 2018</span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=Deutsche+Welle&amp;rft.atitle=Wild+West+museum+in+row+over+Native+American+scalps&amp;rft.date=2014-03-10&amp;rft.au=Knight%2C+Ben&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.de%2Fwild-west-museum-in-row-over-native-american-scalps%2Fa-17498259&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AKarl+May+Museum\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Oltermann-9\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-Oltermann_9-0\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation news\">Oltermann, Philip (10 March 2014). <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.theguardian.com/world/2014/mar/10/german-museum-karl-may-native-american-scalps\">\"German museum in row with US activists over tribal scalps\"</a>. <i>The Guardian</i><span class=\"reference-